main event: An object described as oblong fell from the sky, hitting tall trees before landing in a swamp in Canton, Austinburg, Ohio.
interesting points: The object was observed for 15-20 seconds before disappearing into the trees,The observers were unable to locate the object due to darkness,Two men reported seeing a rectangular-shaped, bright white object hovering over gas pumps shortly after,The object was described as being the size of a small house trailer,Investigations did not find any physical evidence of the objects.
witness description: Two men, aged 66 and 30, observed the object.
